{"thag6.7:0.1":"Theragatha 6.7 ","thag6.7:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thag6.7:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag6.7:0.4":"Katiyanattheragatha ","thag6.7:1.1":"“Utthehi nisida katiyana, ","thag6.7:1.2":"Ma niddabahulo ahu jagarassu; ","thag6.7:1.3":"Ma tam alasam pamattabandhu, ","thag6.7:1.4":"Kuteneva jinatu maccuraja. ","thag6.7:2.1":"Seyyathapi mahasamuddavego, ","thag6.7:2.2":"Evam jatijarativattate tam; ","thag6.7:2.3":"So karohi sudipamattano tvam, ","thag6.7:2.4":"Na hi tanam tava vijjateva annam. ","thag6.7:3.1":"Sattha hi vijesi maggametam, ","thag6.7:3.2":"Sanga jatijarabhaya atitam; ","thag6.7:3.3":"Pubbapararattamappamatto, ","thag6.7:3.4":"Anuyunjassu dalham karohi yogam. ","thag6.7:4.1":"Purimani pamunca bandhanani, ","thag6.7:4.2":"Sanghatikhuramundabhikkhabhoji; ","thag6.7:4.3":"Ma khiddaratinca ma niddam, ","thag6.7:4.4":"Anuyunjittha jhaya katiyana. ","thag6.7:5.1":"Jhayahi jinahi katiyana, ","thag6.7:5.2":"Yogakkhemapathesu kovidosi; ","thag6.7:5.3":"Pappuyya anuttaram visuddhim, ","thag6.7:5.4":"Parinibbahisi varinava joti. ","thag6.7:6.1":"Pajjotakaro parittaramso, ","thag6.7:6.2":"Vatena vinamyate latava; ","thag6.7:6.3":"Evampi tuvam anadiyano, ","thag6.7:6.4":"Maram indasagotta niddhunahi; ","thag6.7:6.5":"So vedayitasu vitarago, ","thag6.7:6.6":"Kalam kankha idheva sitibhuto”ti. ","thag6.7:6.7":"… Katiyano thero …. "}